## File Structure — always place new files here

```
/app
  /dashboard          → Authenticated home (room cards)
  /room/[room_id]     → Room lobby + leaderboard
  /room/[room_id]/trade → Trading terminal
  /join/[room_id]     → Join flow
/components           → Shared UI components
/hooks                → Custom React hooks (useBinanceTicker, etc.)
/actions              → Server Actions only (place_order, close_position, liquidate)
/lib                  → db.ts, auth.ts, types.ts, binance.ts (REST helper), utils.ts
```

